<div class="center"><br />Dave's new Flagstaff pal, Jean-Yves Blondeau</div>
<p>The cloak of fog seemed to encourage the criminal element on Flag today... Saw a guy wedeling down the road on a skateboard wearing a full-coverage motorcycle helmet and a smoking sole.</p>
<p>And a bunch of high school kids hotboxing in a BMW just below the Boatramp.  They must've cracked the windows a hair to lean up the mixture, because I could  smell the reefer from two switchbacks down. Their little secret.</p>
Great ride; cold, foggy, and wet. Bailey weather.  -DU</p>